Still nothing. Zilch.

18:03.790 --> 18:05.530
Why wouldn't he be reported missing?

18:05.540 --> 18:06.825
You tell me.

18:06.830 --> 18:09.913
There's a lot of undocumented
workers In Arizona.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.035
Yes, I know.

18:11.040 --> 18:12.701
