for a long time.

18:18.290 --> 18:20.781
Did any of them drop out
during grade school?

18:20.790 --> 18:22.610
Go back to at least 2004.

18:22.620 --> 18:24.451
2004. 2004...

18:26.330 --> 18:28.036
Second-grader Angel Suarez.

18:28.040 --> 18:29.871
-You got a picture?-Yes.

18:30.120 --> 18:32.497
