Can you send...

18:40.500 --> 18:43.162
_ Yes. Send his mother's
Information to you right now.

18:43.170 --> 18:44.785
You're the best. Bye.

18:45.250 --> 18:46.706
That sounded like good news.

18:46.710 --> 18:48.996
I'm about to call Angel's mom.
He's responding to Morgan.

18:55.250 --> 18:57.115
Okay, Angel, the doc's here.

18:57.120 --> 18:58.496
You want me to stay?

19:02.000 --> 19:03.410
All right, I'll be right outside.

19:03.960 --> 19:05.166
Okay.

19:07.620 --> 19:09.110
Hey, Angel.

19:09.120 --> 19:11.031
You're doing great.

19:11.460 --> 19:13.917
Your mom will be so happy to see you.

19:21.040 --> 19:22.371
Okay.

19:22.380 --> 19:24.746
