29:47.920 --> 29:49.285
And he should have been safe,

29:49.290 --> 29:51.281
except that the French
thought he was a German.

29:56.330 --> 29:58.378
And he was almost executed.

30:05.000 --> 30:07.036
But he showed them a coin.

30:08.830 --> 30:10.991
