30:11.460 --> 30:13.166
It was given to him by a fellow pilot

30:13.170 --> 30:15.491
so that they would never
forget what they shared.

30:17.750 --> 30:19.035
What happened to him?

30:23.580 --> 30:26.708
A French so_ldier _
recognized the msrgnla,

30:27.710 --> 30:29.996
