- -It's okay, you're all right.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.706
You're okay.

40:54.710 --> 40:56.666
Morgan, that's enough! That's enough.

41:54.710 --> 41:56.416
Are you ready, Angel?

42:01.750 --> 42:03.206
Yeah.

42:30.420 --> 42:31.910
Do you always keep one with you?

42:32.210 --> 42:33.279
Yeah.

42:33.790 --> 42:36.953
